@startuml 系统时序图

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 20
skinparam maxmessagesize 60
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

title 系统核心业务时序图

actor "用户" as User
participant "前端界面" as Frontend
participant "API 网关" as Gateway
participant "认证中间件" as AuthMiddleware
participant "权限中间件" as PermMiddleware
participant "业务控制器" as Controller
participant "业务服务" as Service
participant "数据访问层" as DAO
database "数据库" as DB
database "缓存" as Cache
participant "日志服务" as Logger

== 用户注册流程 ==

User -> Frontend: 填写注册信息
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Frontend: 前端表单验证
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /api/auth/register
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMiddleware: 请求预处理
activate AuthMiddleware
AuthMiddleware -> AuthMiddleware: 检查请求头
AuthMiddleware --> Gateway: 继续处理
deactivate AuthMiddleware

Gateway -> Controller: 转发注册请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: 参数验证
Controller -> Service: 调用注册服务
activate Service

Service -> DAO: 检查用户名是否存在
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: 查询结果
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: 用户不存在
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: 密码加密处理
Service -> DAO: 创建用户记录
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO users (...)
activate DB
DB --> DAO: 插入成功
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: 用户创建成功
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: 生成 JWT Token
Service -> Logger: 记录注册日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 返回 Token 和用户信息
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回成功响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK + Token
deactivate Gateway

Frontend -> Frontend: 保存 Token 到本地
Frontend --> User: 显示注册成功
deactivate Frontend

== 用户登录流程 ==

User -> Frontend: 输入用户名和密码
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Gateway: POST /api/auth/login
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Controller: 转发登录请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: 调用登录服务
activate Service

Service -> DAO: 查询用户信息
activate DAO
DAO -> Cache: 检查用户缓存
activate Cache
Cache --> DAO: 缓存未命中
deactivate Cache

DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE username = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: 返回用户信息
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: 用户信息
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: 验证密码
Service -> Service: 生成 JWT Token
Service -> Cache: 缓存用户信息
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 缓存成功
deactivate Cache

Service -> Logger: 记录登录日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 返回 Token 和用户信息
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回成功响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK + Token
deactivate Gateway

Frontend -> Frontend: 保存 Token
Frontend --> User: 跳转到主页
deactivate Frontend

== 业务数据查询流程 ==

User -> Frontend: 请求查询数据
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Gateway: GET /api/business/data?params
note right: 请求头携带 Token
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMiddleware: Token 验证
activate AuthMiddleware
AuthMiddleware -> AuthMiddleware: 解析 Token
AuthMiddleware -> Cache: 验证 Token 有效性
activate Cache
Cache --> AuthMiddleware: Token 有效
deactivate Cache
AuthMiddleware --> Gateway: 认证通过
deactivate AuthMiddleware

Gateway -> PermMiddleware: 权限验证
activate PermMiddleware
PermMiddleware -> Cache: 获取用户权限
activate Cache
Cache --> PermMiddleware: 权限列表
deactivate Cache
PermMiddleware -> PermMiddleware: 检查访问权限
PermMiddleware --> Gateway: 授权通过
deactivate PermMiddleware

Gateway -> Controller: 转发查询请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: 参数验证
Controller -> Service: 调用查询服务
activate Service

Service -> Cache: 检查查询缓存
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 缓存未命中
deactivate Cache

Service -> DAO: 查询数据
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM business_data WHERE ...
activate DB
DB --> DAO: 返回查询结果
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: 数据列表
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: 数据格式化
Service -> Cache: 缓存查询结果
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 缓存成功
deactivate Cache

Service -> Logger: 记录查询日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 返回数据
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回成功响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK + 数据
deactivate Gateway

Frontend -> Frontend: 渲染数据
Frontend --> User: 显示查询结果
deactivate Frontend

== 业务数据录入流程 ==

User -> Frontend: 填写业务数据
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Frontend: 前端验证
Frontend -> Gateway: POST /api/business/data
note right: 请求头携带 Token
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMiddleware: Token 验证
activate AuthMiddleware
AuthMiddleware -> Cache: 验证 Token
activate Cache
Cache --> AuthMiddleware: Token 有效
deactivate Cache
AuthMiddleware --> Gateway: 认证通过
deactivate AuthMiddleware

Gateway -> PermMiddleware: 权限验证
activate PermMiddleware
PermMiddleware -> Cache: 获取用户权限
activate Cache
Cache --> PermMiddleware: 权限列表
deactivate Cache
PermMiddleware -> PermMiddleware: 检查录入权限
PermMiddleware --> Gateway: 授权通过
deactivate PermMiddleware

Gateway -> Controller: 转发录入请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: 数据验证
Controller -> Service: 调用录入服务
activate Service

Service -> Service: 业务规则验证
Service -> DAO: 开启事务
activate DAO

DAO -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
activate DB

DAO -> DB: INSERT INTO business_data (...)
DB --> DAO: 插入成功

DAO -> DB: UPDATE related_table SET ...
DB --> DAO: 更新成功

DAO -> DB: COMMIT
DB --> DAO: 事务提交成功
deactivate DB

DAO --> Service: 数据录入成功
deactivate DAO

Service -> Cache: 清除相关缓存
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 缓存清除成功
deactivate Cache

Service -> Logger: 记录操作日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 返回成功信息
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回成功响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK
deactivate Gateway

Frontend --> User: 显示录入成功
deactivate Frontend

== 业务数据更新流程（含事务回滚） ==

User -> Frontend: 修改业务数据
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Gateway: PUT /api/business/data/:id
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMiddleware: Token 验证
activate AuthMiddleware
AuthMiddleware --> Gateway: 认证通过
deactivate AuthMiddleware

Gateway -> PermMiddleware: 权限验证
activate PermMiddleware
PermMiddleware --> Gateway: 授权通过
deactivate PermMiddleware

Gateway -> Controller: 转发更新请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: 调用更新服务
activate Service

Service -> DAO: 查询原始数据
activate DAO
DAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM business_data WHERE id = ?
activate DB
DB --> DAO: 返回原始数据
deactivate DB
DAO --> Service: 原始数据
deactivate DAO

Service -> Service: 数据对比和验证
Service -> DAO: 开启事务
activate DAO

DAO -> DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
activate DB

DAO -> DB: UPDATE business_data SET ... WHERE id = ?
DB --> DAO: 更新成功

DAO -> DB: UPDATE related_table SET ...
DB --> DAO: 更新失败（约束冲突）
note right: 模拟更新失败场景

DAO -> DB: ROLLBACK
DB --> DAO: 事务回滚成功
deactivate DB

DAO --> Service: 更新失败
deactivate DAO

Service -> Logger: 记录错误日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 返回失败信息
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回错误响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 400 Bad Request
deactivate Gateway

Frontend --> User: 显示错误提示
deactivate Frontend

== 数据分析流程 ==

User -> Frontend: 请求数据分析
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Gateway: GET /api/business/analysis?params
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMiddleware: Token 验证
activate AuthMiddleware
AuthMiddleware --> Gateway: 认证通过
deactivate AuthMiddleware

Gateway -> PermMiddleware: 权限验证
activate PermMiddleware
PermMiddleware --> Gateway: 授权通过
deactivate PermMiddleware

Gateway -> Controller: 转发分析请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: 调用分析服务
activate Service

Service -> Cache: 检查分析缓存
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 缓存命中
deactivate Cache

Service -> Logger: 记录分析日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 返回分析结果
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回成功响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK + 分析数据
deactivate Gateway

Frontend -> Frontend: 渲染图表
Frontend --> User: 显示分析报告
deactivate Frontend

== 用户登出流程 ==

User -> Frontend: 点击登出
activate Frontend

Frontend -> Gateway: POST /api/auth/logout
activate Gateway

Gateway -> AuthMiddleware: Token 验证
activate AuthMiddleware
AuthMiddleware --> Gateway: 认证通过
deactivate AuthMiddleware

Gateway -> Controller: 转发登出请求
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: 调用登出服务
activate Service

Service -> Cache: 删除用户缓存
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 缓存删除成功
deactivate Cache

Service -> Cache: 将 Token 加入黑名单
activate Cache
Cache --> Service: 黑名单添加成功
deactivate Cache

Service -> Logger: 记录登出日志
activate Logger
Logger -> DB: INSERT INTO logs (...)
deactivate Logger

Service --> Controller: 登出成功
deactivate Service

Controller --> Gateway: 返回成功响应
deactivate Controller

Gateway --> Frontend: 200 OK
deactivate Gateway

Frontend -> Frontend: 清除本地 Token
Frontend --> User: 跳转到登录页
deactivate Frontend

@enduml
